OL,5, Shoppers and retailers are set for a   
OL,6, "challenging" year ahead, according to 
OL,7, a leading trade body.                  
OL,9,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC) has
OL,10,Fwarned that higher living costs will   
OL,11,Fcontinue to squeeze household budgets. 
OL,13,FIts boss pointed out that firms will   
OL,14,Falso face higher business rates as well
OL,15,Fas potential disruption to shipments   
OL,16,Fvia the Red Sea.                       
OL,18,FDespite a flat Christmas, other figures
OL,19,Fsuggest that people are still willing  
OL,20,Fto spend more on holidaysin 2024.      
